# The pose landmarker .task model is NOT tracked here on purpose — it's a
# multi-MB binary and you're pushing from mobile data. The CI workflow
# (.github/workflows/build-apk.yml) downloads it directly on the runner if
# it's missing from the repo, so you don't need to push it at all. If you'd
# rather commit it (e.g. for offline/reproducible builds), just remove this
# line and `git add -f` the file.
app/src/main/assets/*.task
